                "type": "rich_text",
                "block_id": "+RQWU",
                "elements": [
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "I think that was the complaint about the initial release. In the demos they showed what looked like composable tags, but the star wars sets come with limited tags in terms of number of tags (I think the x-wing has one) and functionality, hardcoded to \"act like an xwing\" or \"act like a tie fighter\", which adds a lot of baked in assumptions and limits creativity"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],
